<br>
I was lucky in that my enchanter has the cloak of confusion and enchanter arms, both very nice items.  And my druid has a druid doll given me by Danni when she retired from EQ.  I think I have a full set of crowns and squires a knight and a few pages of WoW and a couple funney money.  <br>
<br>
For me it's a very safe place to retreat to when I need to and a nice place to park my enchanter when she is not needed.<br>
